title: 'Making the Cut'
description:
'Making the Cut' is Amazon's version of 'Project Runway' and features not only Tim Gunn and Heidi Klum, but also the valuable adds of Naomi Campbell and Nicole Richie.

Hosts: Juliet Litman and Justin Verrier
